      <p>
         <fig>
            <image placement="break"
                   width="900"
                   href="../attachments/102432718/109942246.png"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>You can provide the following information on the Qualifications and Benefits page:</p>
      <p>
         <table>
            <tgroup cols="2">
               <colspec colname="col1"/>
               <colspec colname="col2"/>
               <thead>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Fields</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Description</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </thead>
               <tbody>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Bundle Name</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Select the bundle name for the set of products you want to buy.</p>
                        <p>Mention the package name for the set of products, for which package is created, you want to buy.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Product Name</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Add products or categories in the Product Name column. For adding products or categories, please refer to the <xref href="../adding-products_102432695_102432695/102432695_1.xml"
                                 format="dita">Adding Products</xref> section. Products are the list of products that are purchased by customers at the bundle level.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>UOM (Unit Of Measure)</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>It defaults to Each.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Type</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Auto-populated based on selected products or categories.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Unit</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Enter the unit of products that customer purchases.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Unit Price</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Enter the price of the products per unit.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Extended Price</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>It is the auto-calculated price for the whole unit of the product.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Bundle Price</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Aggregated price of the products which are grouped in the bundle.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Save</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Click Save to save the made changes.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
            </tgroup>
         </table>
      </p>
      <p>You can also import the bundle product by duplicate the entire bundle to perform the following actions:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>To add multiple bundles to the programs</li>
         <li>To edit the start and end dates</li>
         <li>To add new products to the bundles</li>
      </ul>
      <p>For more information about Tiered qualifications and benefits, please refer to the <xref href="../qualifications_and_benefi_102432700/102432700.xml"
               format="dita">Qualifications and Benefits</xref> section.</p>
      <p>Importing Benefit Line Items</p>
      <p>For more information about importing the individual section of the Package Saving Program, please refer to the <xref href="../importing_benefit_line_it_102432715/102432715.xml"
               format="dita">Importing Benefit Line Items</xref> section.</p>
